; Fixture journal for /api/month-summary integration tests.
; Covers:
;   - Salary income paid into bank
;   - Expense paid via debit (assets contra)
;   - Expense paid via credit card (liability contra)
;   - Card payment (asset -> liability, no expense)
;   - Installment per ADR-010 — single tx with full amount + parcelamento: tag
;   - One card under each of the three accepted spellings
;     (cartão, cartao, credit-card) so the aggregate sums them all.

; Opening balances (so --historical has something to start from).
2025-12-31 * Opening balance
    assets:bank                     5000.00
    equity:opening

; ── April 2026 — the month we test against ──────────────────────────

2026-04-01 * Salary
    assets:bank                    10000.00
    income:salary

2026-04-05 * Mercado (debit)
    expenses:groceries               300.00
    assets:bank

2026-04-10 * Restaurante (credit card)
    expenses:dining                  150.00
    liabilities:cartão:nubank

2026-04-12 * Streaming (credit card, ascii spelling)
    expenses:entertainment            29.90
    liabilities:cartao:itau

2026-04-14 * SaaS (credit card, english spelling)
    expenses:services                 49.90
    liabilities:credit-card:amex

; ADR-010: an installment is recorded as ONE transaction on the original
; purchase date with the FULL amount as expense and as card-liability,
; tagged with `parcelamento:`. Subsequent invoice lines for that same
; purchase are skipped on import.
2026-04-20 * Eletrodomestico parcelado  ; parcelamento: ELECTROLUX 1/10
    expenses:moradia:equipamentos    1200.00
    liabilities:cartão:nubank

; Card payment — settles previous-month balance. Must NOT count as expense.
2026-04-25 * Pagamento fatura cartão
    liabilities:cartão:nubank        500.00
    assets:bank
